Smoked Chicken BBQ Pizza (on the Grill) with @HomeRunInn Pizza GIVEAWAY ALERT (CLOSED) Congratulations to @clw215  for winning!
 .
You know what I love pretty much more than anything – when it comes to grilling, of course?!? When two (delicious) worlds melt together. Few things excite me more than smoked BBQ chicken, but when you layer that tender, juicy smoked BBQ Chicken with @HomeRunInn grilled pizza? Well that’s grilling magic, my friends.
 .
This Smoked Chicken BBQ pizza is sure to be a hit with anyone who tries it! And because Home Run Inn is so sure you’re gonna love what we came up with here, they’re giving away a grill, a year’s worth of frozen pizza, $1,000 in cash, and a @HomeRunInn swag bag to one lucky winner. All you have to do to win is:
1. Follow @HomeRunInn on Instagram
2. Tag 2 friends in the comment section of a @HomeRunInn official giveaway post in their Instagram feed (posts will be marked as official giveaway posts)

We have teamed up for an amazing GIVEAWAY; St Pierre is looking for America’s Favorite Grilling Recipe!
.
How to enter:
.
Upload a photo or video of your grilling recipe using St Pierre brioche to Instagram, tag @stpierreusa and use the hashtag #AmericasFavoriteGrillingRecipe.
.
St Pierre will choose their top 10 entries and send them to me (GRILLNATION) and then I will choose my top 3.
.

The chicken got shredded and I assembled the BBQ Chicken Melts right before I easily set the Ninja Woodfire XL to the grill function to MED for 6 minutes.
